title: The Magicians,The Magicians King, The Magicians Land by Lev Gros
description:
Each book is a single mp3 file, each book is read by Mark Bramhall

The Magicians is a trilogy of fantasy novels by the American author Lev Grossman. It tells the story of Quentin Coldwater, a young man from Brooklyn who discovers and attends a college of magic in upstate New York, Brakebills College for Magical Pedagogy. He loves a series of books called "Fillory and Further," which involve the children of the Chatwin family discovering a Narnia-esque land called Fillory.

The Magicians (2009)
The Magicians King (2011)
The Magicians Land (2014)
